### ===== JWT AUTHENTICATION API TESTS =====

### 1. Register new user
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "role": "User"
}

### 2. Register admin user
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "confirmPassword": "admin123",
  "role": "Admin"
}

### 3. Login with user credentials
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Login with admin credentials
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. Test protected endpoint - Get customers (requires token)
GET https://localhost:7211/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Test login with wrong credentials
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 7. Test register with existing email
POST https://localhost:7211/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}

### 8. Test access without token (should return 401)
GET https://localhost:7211/api/customers

### ===== NOTES =====
# 1. Sau khi login thành công, copy token từ response
# 2. Paste token vào "YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE" ở request #5
# 3. Token có thời hạn 60 phút (cấu hình trong appsettings.json)